20:18.011 --> 20:21.261
<b>The Ryugu Kingdom is attending the Reverie!</b>

20:21.431 --> 20:22.891
<b>Prince Fukaboshi!</b>

20:23.051 --> 20:28.331
<b><i>Moonfish! Moonfish!
I wanna have fun on land!</i></b>

20:28.331 --> 20:31.271
<b>It's so bright on land-<i>do-re-mi-fa-so</i>!</b>

20:31.691 --> 20:33.271
<b>Let's go, guys.</b>

20:33.271 --> 20:34.731
<b>Moonfish!</b>

20:37.281 --> 20:39.041
<b>Garp-<i>sama</i>!</b>

20:40.361 --> 20:43.061
<b>I thought I was gonna die in the deep sea!</b>

20:44.761 --> 20:47.601
<b>RYUGU PALACE</b>

20:44.911 --> 20:47.741
<b>Hey, Princess-<i>san</i>! Come out!</b>

20:49.951 --> 20:51.851
<b>Okay, Shirahoshi.</b>

20:52.621 --> 20:55.161
<b>Let's go to Mariejois!</b>

20:58.551 --> 20:59.351
<b>Yes...</b>

21:03.381 --> 21:05.031
<b>So this is the surface!</b>

21:09.141 --> 21:11.181
<b>It's Mermaid Princess-<i>sama</i>!</b>

21:15.771 --> 21:17.451
<b><i><i>It has been 200 years</i></i></b>

21:17.451 --> 21:20.091
<b><i>since the Ryugu Kingdom began 
affiliating with the World Government,</i></b>

21:20.691 --> 21:24.741
<b><i><i>but they have attended the Reverie
only once before.</i></i></b>

21:24.781 --> 21:28.371
<b><i>So this is indeed a big deal.</i></b>

21:29.431 --> 21:32.681
<b>HOLYLAND OF MARIEJOIS</b>

21:36.171 --> 21:37.121
<b>Clank.</b>

21:38.341 --> 21:42.941
<b>Sakazuki-<i>san</i> told me to find you
and kick you out...</b>

21:46.391 --> 21:47.801
<b>You wanna fight me?</b>

21:50.011 --> 21:53.351
<b>Give me a break! I don't want to!</b>

21:53.481 --> 21:56.811
<b>It's not like you wanna destroy 
the conference, right?</b>

21:58.981 --> 22:00.771
<b>No, I don't...</b>

22:01.321 --> 22:03.361
<b>What I want to destroy is...</b>

22:04.951 --> 22:06.471
<b>...the system.</b>

22:08.201 --> 22:11.741
<b>Thank you for the meal.
It was delicious!</b>

22:12.051 --> 22:16.591
<b>You had a long journey.
How is the old man Vegapunk doing?</b>

22:16.871 --> 22:22.761
<b>Well, of course I couldn't lay eyes on it
but he has completed something incredible.</b>

22:22.921 --> 22:24.811
<b>Oh, what is it like?</b>

22:27.681 --> 22:31.841
<b>We no longer need the 
Seven Warlords of the Sea!</b>

22:33.851 --> 22:36.721
<b>You're crazy! Really!</b>

22:38.171 --> 22:42.191
<b>By the way, the food here is delicious,
just as I thought!</b>

22:42.191 --> 22:43.911
<b>Why don't you eat something?</b>

22:44.441 --> 22:48.041
<b>Are you still fasting?</b>

22:45.721 --> 22:51.761
<b>RYOKUGYU - AN ADMIRAL 
OF THE NAVY HEADQUARTERS</b>

22:49.571 --> 22:53.981
<b>If some young lady helps me, I would eat!</b>

22:54.451 --> 23:00.081
<b>I'm so lazy. I haven't eaten 
anything for three years!</b>

23:09.721 --> 23:11.701
<b><i><i>The Revolutionary Army led by Sabo commences</i></i></b>

23:11.701 --> 23:15.611
<b><i>their operation to infiltrate Mariejois for 
the purpose of changing history forever!</i></b>

23:15.851 --> 23:19.061
<b><i><i>Meanwhile, the dazzling view of 
the beautiful surface world brings</i></i></b>

23:19.061 --> 23:20.701
<b><i>tears to Shirahoshi's eyes</i></b>

23:20.701 --> 23:25.611
<b><i>and gives her a wish that marks a new chapter
in the Fish-Men's history!</i></b>

23:25.741 --> 23:27.011
<b>On the next episode of One Piece!</b>

23:27.011 --> 23:30.291
<b>"One Step Forward for Her Dream! 
Shirahoshi Goes Out in the Sun!"</b>

23:30.291 --> 23:32.731
<b>I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!</b>
